snippet.textDisplay:
I've seen and have a completely new understanding for who Kobe was due to all of these clips I've never seen before.

Few of you may be able to see it, but Kobe lived very much in isolation compared to what we've seen on screen. He was on his way to living his life after retirement.

If you understand the grudge MJ held throughout his career, you'll understand what Kobe meant when he said he didn't care what happened with basketball after he was finished. He let go that part of his life and was ready to move on... I couldn't understand before, but now I do.
